headline: Generac Recognized for Excellence in Design with 2024 GOOD DESIGN Awards
summary: Generac Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: GNRC), a leading global designer, manufacturer and provider of energy technology solutions and other power products, has been recognized with GOOD DESIGN Awards in 2024 for the Generac XG04045 Liquid-Cooled Home Standby Generator and the Generac GP7500E Dual Fuel Portable Generator.
